707241f-a.title: Brooklyn: Washington Ave. - Flushing Ave.
707241f-a.text:
Wallabout Market, Brooklyn, Wiashington Avenue, east side, north from Flushing Ave. From this market most of the vegetables for Brooklyn's retail stores are distributed.
October 11, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
